reviewText: Cute video with a great lesson
I personally can't get past the fact that these are cockroaches but my kids love this series and like VeggieTales, they have Saturday morning fun and Sunday morning values....
My kids love this movie!  My son is 3 and my daughter is 5...they can't get enough.
Wow,this is high quality stuff! The story line and gags are great. This is as good as pixar. Keep it the good work!!
